subject: Rogers Cup (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Jack Sock of the United States defeated Jurgen Melzer, 6-1, 6-3, in the first round at the Rogers Cup in Toronto, setting up a match with the big-serving Milos Raonic.
